{"tid":102134,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點睇開係市區既美食車檔主望兩年回本","createTime":"2017-01-31T11:47:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-31T16:11:59.000Z","uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"212844bc0d437386fab6ea07c5df2b9468dd9748","tid":102134,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T11:47:09.000Z","msg":"果檔野前後用左一百萬set up fee 學者分析每月要14萬營運成本<br />\n<br />\n家庭式經營餃子店「有得餃」亦首次在公開場合，出售寓意五代同堂的「五色餃」。老闆廖震豪稱，中環年宵出售的「五色餃」，將會是「即包、即滾、即食」，保證最新鮮，售價與美食車開業後一樣是40元六隻。<br />\n<br />\n係咪咁好賣<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/CVpFUZlWEAAw6UR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FCVpFUZlWEAAw6UR.png&h=087e4205&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bbe09b5c44f7415fc76f9986d04b3f7071785def","tid":102134,"uid":65056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T12:27:21.000Z","msg":"保守d 計佢每份淨賺30蚊<br />\n<br />\n想breakeven 要每日賣$140,000 / 30 days / 30 = 156份 （呢個應該唔難）<br />\n<br />\n要回本即係賺$1,000,000<br />\n<br />\n即係$1,000,000 / 2 years / 365 days / 30 = 46 份<br />\n<br />\n想每日淨賺只要每日賣多過202份就可以<br />\n<br />\n我既意見係真係好好賺"},{"pid":"da626472b52a95ac2d8a0481151a6c5c81e394bd","tid":102134,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T12:32:25.000Z","msg":"40元六隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0797931bf74f1f36a47138d6d8a74780ac3c4dce","tid":102134,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T12:32:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"170282445981b0ee4941fce95f17ad5f703af6e3","tid":102134,"uid":44454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T12:36:2